OL,3,CGrieving son fined hundreds after
OL,4,Cfather's funeral overran by 13 minutes
OL,6,FA grieving son from Somerset says he's
OL,7,Fangry after being fined hundreds of
OL,8,Fpounds when his father's funeral
OL,9,Fservice overran by a matter of minutes.
OL,11,FIn September 2024, a service was held
OL,12,Fat Taunton Crematorium to remember Rob
OL,13,FScurlock's dad William who died in
OL,14,FAugust at the age of 79.
OL,16,FThe family's funeral was the last of
OL,17,Fthe day, however they were fined #432
OL,18,Ffor running 13 minutes over their time
OL,19,Fslot.
