OL,4,Cfather's funeral overran by 13 minutes
OL,6,FRob told ITV West Country: "It was
OL,7,Fsupposed to be a sombre sort of
OL,8,Fgoodbye for a loved one. Losing a
OL,9,Fparent is already tough enough.
OL,11,F"It wasn't a nice experience and
OL,12,Fthat's tarnished what should be a
OL,13,Flasting fond memory. It's quite
OL,14,Fshameful to be honest.
