OL,6,F"It's not something we would expect
OL,7,Ffrom our local authority when we're
OL,8,Fgoing through such a difficult moment
OL,9,Fin our lives and planning what is
OL,10,Fsupposed to be one of the most
OL,11,Fimportant things you can do for a
OL,12,Fparent when you've got to say goodbye
OL,13,Fto them."
OL,15,FSomerset Council, which runs the site,
OL,16,Fsays funeral times must be strictly
OL,17,Fcontrolled, but it's reviewing the
OL,18,Fcharges.
