OL,4,Cfather's funeral overran by 13 minutes
OL,6,FIn a statement, it told ITV West
OL,7,FCountry: "The Crematorium aims to make
OL,8,Fevery service ` the last memory for
OL,9,Fthe bereaved ` run as smoothly and
OL,10,Fsensitively as possible.
OL,12,F"Times for each funeral have to be
OL,13,Fstrictly controlled to make sure other
OL,14,Fservices can take place at the
OL,15,Fallotted time. This is particularly
OL,16,Fimportant if the service is being
OL,17,Fstreamed. There is the option to
OL,18,Fextend the service.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
