OL,6,F"The Crematorium is under new
OL,7,Fmanagement and charges for overrunning
OL,8,Fare being reviewed and will be
OL,9,Freflected in the revised pricing
OL,10,Fstructure from March.
OL,12,F"If the bereaved have any concerns
OL,13,Fabout costs they are encouraged to
OL,14,Fcontact the Crematorium direct to
OL,15,Fdiscuss. The fees and charges are
OL,16,Fpublicly available."
OL,18,FRob says the experience, will forever
OL,19,Ftaint his father's final farewell.
