OL,6,FHe added: "I've never disagreed with
OL,7,Fthe council's viewpoint, I do know
OL,8,Fthat they have a decent structure to
OL,9,Frunning a day to day operation.
OL,11,F"However, the fines do need to be fair
OL,12,Fand they do need to be tolerable for
OL,13,Ffamilies that are already struggling
OL,14,Ffinancially. Also it has to be looked
OL,15,Fat on a day by day basis. It just
OL,16,Fneeds a bit more common sense."
